Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都高5号线北池袋附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现超自然灾害源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类型B  种别为火车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉找不到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我…都是我不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把事情和我们说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理班立刻出动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情明白了  我这就派调查班过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧  我们一定会找到黄泉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…不会那样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  快接  求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}您所拨打的电话在服务区外或处于关机状态未能接通…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉！不要出事啊  黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你回话吧！黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这堵车也太严重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场在高速公路上  受其影响的结果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不单是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是市谷的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们抄近路！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是以黄泉为目标在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有黄泉在才会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在为妈妈过世而哭泣的时候  是黄泉温柔地安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次本该我去支撑她才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐你很喜欢那位姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你就继续相信她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐如果也喜欢神乐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意一定会传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  美红
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁都会有摩擦或冷遇的时候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想姐姐也一定觉得是需要神乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  吃了这个打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有工作对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！土宫神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求饶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了  早晚要扒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人的事情真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散播这场灾难的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是来复仇的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种浅薄的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是来贯彻职责而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有要战斗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作为一个旁观者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该弄架直升机啦  直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京市内用汽车出动本身就是个错误的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是常有需要直升机的任务还得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么换骑摩托怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黄泉的情报了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到点线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能证明她是无罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先解决眼前的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  这就是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所拨打的电话在服务区外或处于关机状态未能接通…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人的话没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  那人会回来的  绝对会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪相信黄泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不为我们所知的敌人存在  是他把黄泉害成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没有证据  但我找到这样的可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该更相信她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸…尸体！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是类型D！各自拿上家伙准备应战！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现一群魍魎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在机动中队队员遗体身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二连三的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕暗处有人设局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设局？究竟是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打伤黄泉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对一切都是他干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello～神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么谏山她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策室呼叫处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻起把谏山黄泉认定为超自然灾害源类型A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此开始除灵  将其排除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟从哪冒出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体成员聚集到一处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备还击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭纲  你去追谏山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这里就由我们挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这里有我们就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  一击就打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  大家别死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话应该由我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同沟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同沟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于地下的命脉隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉在这下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有梯子  下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们根本就不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱庭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  黄泉怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的变成恶灵了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…变不回来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又分出了一条隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带上一只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事的话我就会立刻赶过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去对面找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪你也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明医院一直都不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不定决心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出要摆怎样的面孔来见我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一辈子不能正常行动  连话都讲不出的杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能交往嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找加害你的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也在做见你的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都好啦  这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭在人世间散播死亡污秽的家伙正是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就是死亡的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不杀我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会杀了他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！这和一骑没关系吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是来浪费我和纪之的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  可以住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我就可以住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  你再不赶快他可就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之…杀了…谏山！动手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放弃她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快用那个来杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了纪之  你喜欢飞镖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜欢飞镖的…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之…杀了她…纪之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是单倍区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是双倍区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是三倍区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…住手！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧黄泉！快停手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小纪找到黄泉的话会战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别杀他！要杀就杀我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不了手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪也喜欢黄泉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  找到黄泉后要想办法救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我…杀了我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪…之…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煤气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度就想甩掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  以为杀掉我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱…红莲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吧  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系  马上就让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…黄泉…姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  原来是土宫阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到  你竟然会深陷迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷茫早就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话  喰灵  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命运混乱」
